-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-06-21T14:39:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/south-african-central-bank-appoints-ford-hoon-as-financial-service-head.html

          
          
             South Africaâ€™s central bank 
appointed Naidene Ford-Hoon as head of its financial services 
department, according to a statement on its website today.  
 Ford-Hoon will begin on July 19 and will replace Gerrie 
Terblanche, who retires at the end of next month, the 
Pretoria-based Reserve Bank said. The head of the financial 
services department is also the chief financial officer of the 
Reserve Bank, it said.  
          
          


  


        